     - *ett* (determiner of *fönster*) → distance 2
     - *litet* (adjective of *fönster*) → distance 2
     - *fönster* → distance 1
     - *som* (relative pronoun) → distance 1
     - *tipsar* (head of the relative clause)
       - *om* → distance 2
       - *andra* (determiner of *program*) → distance 2
       - *program* → distance 2

